---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Research">
  <section class="py-8 space-y-4">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Research</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">
      This page highlights my research interests, publications, and ongoing projects in the field of machine learning, data science, and AI.
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-1">
      <li>Deep Learning for Computer Vision</li>
      <li>Natural Language Processing</li>
      <li>Scalable ML Systems</li>
      <li>Applied AI in Real-world Products</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mt-4">
      For more details or collaboration opportunities, feel free to reach out!
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
